<a name="ex02" ID="title">Keyboard shortcuts</a><br><br>
As you'll get more confidence with this application, you might like using the following keyboard shortcuts,
for speeding up your movements.<br><br>
<table cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0 valign="top">
<tr>
<td WIDTH="15"></td><td STYLE="color:#005CB6;">ALT + <b>I</b></td><td WIDTH="15"></td><td>Initialize generators according to current method</td></tr>
<td WIDTH="15"></td><td STYLE="color:#005CB6;">ALT + <b>S</b></td><td WIDTH="15"></td><td>Stop current drawing process</td></tr>
<td WIDTH="15"></td><td STYLE="color:#005CB6;">ALT + <b>PLUS</b></td><td WIDTH="15"></td><td>Increment depth by one</td></tr>
<td WIDTH="15"></td><td STYLE="color:#005CB6;">ALT + <b>MINUS</b></td><td WIDTH="15"></td><td>Decrement depth by one</td></tr>
<td WIDTH="15"></td><td STYLE="color:#005CB6;">CTRL + SHIFT + <b>A</b></td><td WIDTH="15"></td><td>Add circle</td></tr>
<td WIDTH="15"></td><td STYLE="color:#005CB6;">CTRL + ALT + <b>D</b></td><td WIDTH="15"></td><td>Open dictionary panel</td></tr>
<td WIDTH="15"></td><td STYLE="color:#005CB6;">CTRL + <b>E</b></td><td WIDTH="15"></td><td>Edit circle (current selection)</td></tr>
<td WIDTH="15"></td><td STYLE="color:#005CB6;">CTRL + ALT + <b>F</b></td><td WIDTH="15"></td><td>Render image plane</td></tr>
<td WIDTH="15"></td><td STYLE="color:#005CB6;">CTRL + ALT + <b>I</b></td><td WIDTH="15"></td><td>Save image plane into a file</td></tr>
<td WIDTH="15"></td><td STYLE="color:#005CB6;">CTRL + <b>K</b></td><td WIDTH="15"></td><td>Open generators check panel</td></tr>
<td WIDTH="15"></td><td STYLE="color:#005CB6;">CTRL + <b>L</b></td><td WIDTH="15"></td><td>Open seeds list panel</td></tr>
<td WIDTH="15"></td><td STYLE="color:#005CB6;">CTRL + SHIFT + <b>M</b></td><td WIDTH="15"></td><td>Add Mobius map</td></tr>
<td WIDTH="15"></td><td STYLE="color:#005CB6;">CTRL + ALT + <b>M</b></td><td WIDTH="15"></td><td>Open current method panel</td></tr>
<td WIDTH="15"></td><td STYLE="color:#005CB6;">CTRL + <b>N</b></td><td WIDTH="15"></td><td>New enviroment</td></tr>
<td WIDTH="15"></td><td STYLE="color:#005CB6;">CTRL + ALT + <b>P</b></td><td WIDTH="15"></td><td>Open last used plugin panel</td></tr>
<td WIDTH="15"></td><td STYLE="color:#005CB6;">CTRL + ALT + <b>R</b></td><td WIDTH="15"></td><td>Render source plane</td></tr>
<td WIDTH="15"></td><td STYLE="color:#005CB6;">CTRL + ALT + <b>S</b></td><td WIDTH="15"></td><td>Save source plane into a file</td></tr>
<td WIDTH="15"></td><td STYLE="color:#005CB6;">CTRL + ALT + <b>T</b></td><td WIDTH="15"></td><td>Open terminal console</td></tr>
<td WIDTH="15"></td><td STYLE="color:#005CB6;">CTRL + <b>U</b></td><td WIDTH="15"></td><td>Toggle off current disk(s) selection</td></tr>
</tr>
</table>
